penicillin, whether or not you

00:23:05.330 --> 00:23:08.300
know the structure or not, but
the most important part of

00:23:08.300 --> 00:23:10.440
this structure is the
four-membered ring here, the

00:23:10.440 --> 00:23:14.400
beta-lactam, and this was the
first time I thought I could

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:17.370
actually understand how a
molecule worked because I knew

00:23:17.370 --> 00:23:19.130
something about chemistry.

00:23:19.130 --> 00:23:22.620
So, for example with penicillin
what it does is it

00:23:22.620 --> 00:23:26.710
inhibits an enzyme that builds
the cell wall in bacteria, the

00:23:26.710 --> 00:23:30.250
bacterial cell wall, and if I
thought about what I'd learned

00:23:30.250 --> 00:23:32.230
in chemistry -- some of you know
this from high school,

00:23:32.230 --> 00:23:34.980
some of you will be very
familiar with this soon, is

00:23:34.980 --> 00:23:37.230
that this carbon here,
for example, is

00:23:37.230 --> 00:23:38.720
bonded to three things.

00:23:38.720 --> 00:23:43.640
Does anyone know what angle
those would like to be at?

00:23:43.640 --> 00:23:44.620
120.

00:23:44.620 --> 00:23:46.930
They want to get as far away
from each other possible, the

00:23:46.930 --> 00:23:48.640
ideal angle is 120.

00:23:48.640 --> 00:23:51.270
But what we have here is a
four-membered ring, so what

00:23:51.270 --> 00:23:54.660
angle does that have
to be, that bond?

00:23:54.660 --> 00:23:56.140
90 degrees.

00:23:56.140 --> 00:23:58.750
So, we have a problem here if
we're thinking about keeping

00:23:58.750 --> 00:24:01.120
things at the lowest energy,
so there's a lot of ring

00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:02.410
strain in the system.

00:24:02.410 --> 00:24:05.130
And I was incredibly excited
that I could look at that and

00:24:05.130 --> 00:24:07.530
realize it and say "Wow, that's
why it's so reactive,

00:24:07.530 --> 00:24:10.470
that's why it's such a good
medication," because when it

00:24:10.470 --> 00:24:13.590
comes into contact with these
bacterial cell wall building

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:17.420
