react with this

00:24:17.420 --> 00:24:19.690
four-membered ring and
open up the ring and

00:24:19.690 --> 00:24:21.470
relieve that ring strain.

00:24:21.470 --> 00:24:24.560
So, now the angles can open up
all the way to 120 if it wants

00:24:24.560 --> 00:24:26.740
to, and there's no way it's
going to form that ring again,

00:24:26.740 --> 00:24:29.550
right, because it's not going
to back to those 90 degree

00:24:29.550 --> 00:24:30.970
angles, if it can help it.

00:24:30.970 --> 00:24:33.940
So now, the enzyme is locked
up with the penicillin

00:24:33.940 --> 00:24:37.380
molecule, no more bacterial cell
wall being built, and the

00:24:37.380 --> 00:24:40.060
penicillin has effectively
killed the bacteria.

00:24:40.060 --> 00:24:42.500
